        <mxCell id="note-academic-struct" value="Note: Color coding - Blue: Core academic entities | Green: Related entities | Orange: Assignment entities&#xa;&#xa;External Relationships (not shown):&#xa;- departments.head_id → users (from User Management)&#xa;- sections.teacher_id → users (from User Management)&#xa;- sections.floor_id → floors (from Facilities)&#xa;- section_modules.module_id → modules (from Learning Materials)&#xa;- section_modules.assigned_by → users (from User Management)&#xa;&#xa;Internal Relationships:&#xa;- departments → departments_information (1:N), departments → subjects (1:N), sections → section_modules (1:N)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff9e6;strokeColor=#d79b00;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;" parent="1" vertex="1">
